text: Sydney George Nelson (born December 9, 1932) is an American politician in the state of Minnesota. He served in the Minnesota House of Representatives from 1991–1992 and 1993–1994. He was previously a Wadena County, Minnesota county commissioner, serving from 1986 to 1991.https://www.leg.state.mn.us/legdb/fulldetail?ID=10456 ==References== Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Minnesota Democrats Category:County commissioners in Minnesota Category:Members of the Minnesota House of Representatives
